1. *Informacije* koje dobijamo su veoma važne. (The information we receive is very important.)
2. On nudi *informacije* o njegovom poslu. (He provides information about his job.)
3. Svi su tražili *informacije* o njegovom istorijatu. (Everyone was looking for information about his background.)
4. Imamo potrebne *informacije* o tome. (We have the necessary information about it.)
5. Oni nisu imali dovoljno *informacija*. (They didn't have enough information.)
6. Ona je u potrazi za *informacijama*. (She is looking for information.)
7. Nisam imao dovoljno *informacija* o tome. (I didn't have enough information about it.)